    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You can use your innate magic to create minor illusions that augment your efforts at trickery and deceit.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Gnome, gnome magic racial trait.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>As long as you have at least one spell-like ability unused from your gnome magic racial trait, you gain a +2 racial bonus on all Bluff, Disguise, and Sleight of Hand checks you make. At 10th level, these bonuses increase to +4.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>This feat counts as the Deceitful feat for the purposes of all prerequisites.",
